messages:
Title: feat:folder-view-implemented
Body: This PR introduces a dynamic folder structure view, allowing users to:  
- Add files to specific folders.  
- View and organize folders and files in a tree-like structure.  
- Efficiently manage and navigate the folder hierarchy.  


## Screenshots  
**Before:**  
![Screenshot 2024-11-26 181919](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cfdab696-e086-49d9-830f-f13355cfa93c)


**After:**  
![Screenshot 2024-11-26 182230](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/543afc13-737b-4bd5-a7af-46ef18b161b9)

## Outcome  
The folder structure enhances clarity, organization, and usability, providing a seamless experience for file management.
